channel.title: Can someone test something for me?
channel.description:
I'm trying to get a webclient to just work, and I am using a blank server to test a connection. I port forwarded, I am using no-ip and I keep trying to connect via no-ip, but it isnt loading up the server. I fully portforwarded and I think it has something to do with the no-ip client I am using.
I want to know if you can get a good connection through to the server, and can play it.(server [url=http://pdscape.webs.com/PdScape.htm]here[/url]).
:| Please help me?
